title: Twilight - Complete Series - For Your iPod
description:
How To Add To Your iPod:

1. Plug in your iPod. 

2. Your iPod should show up as a drive on your computer. 
*If it doesn't, open iTunes and enable disk use on your iPod. 

3. Install WordPod - http://www.mediafire.com/?4tmi3mmngr3

4. Open WordPod. Add the Twilight .txt files. Press OK for the next 2 windows. 

5. Click the Sync button.

6. To read the books, just select the "Extras" option in the main screen of your iPod, then select "Notes." 

7. Get a sandwich. For the smooth, salty, yet sweet taste you enjoy, make it a P,B&J. Mmm.. mmm. That's a great sandwich. In fact. I'm gonna go get one right now.
